data.description: Nitish Kumar will again take oath as the chief minister of Bihar on Thursday, a day after he resigned from the post citing corruption cases against RJD leaders of the Grand Alliance, including Tejashwi Yadav.

data.title: Nitish Kumar to take oath as Bihar Chief Minister at 10 am on Thursday
